{"id":18370696,"date":"2025-08-27T17:35:00","date_gmt":"2025-08-27T12:05:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/?p=18370696"},"modified":"2025-08-26T11:09:17","modified_gmt":"2025-08-26T05:39:17","slug":"bcom-with-acca-help-you-work-abroad","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/bcom-with-acca-help-you-work-abroad","title":{"rendered":"Can a BCom with ACCA Help You Work Abroad? Exploring Global Prospects\u00a0"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Is moving abroad the new fashion now? It certainly appears to be a trend that everyone is following. We bet that everyone will have at least one close-knit loved one who has moved abroad or is in the process of doing so. However, most of them go there to study and then seek employment. But what if we told you that you could work abroad with BCom and ACCA international opportunities?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, you heard it right. The ACCA global job prospects are a very promising endeavor that learners can look forward to. Rather than moving towards a future with ambiguity, this program will provide a secure solution with no looking back. However, this requires extensive research to determine which country works best, how financially secure it can be, and other factors. This well-curated blog will provide you with all the details you need to help take this dream forward.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Give this a read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/difference-between-ca-and-acca\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>What is the difference between CA and ACCA?<\/strong><\/a><strong><\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Understanding BCom with ACCA\u00a0<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/bcom-course-details\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">BCom<\/a> is a three-year UG program mainly focused on the subjects that lay the foundation towards accounting, economics, taxation and business management.&nbsp; It is one of the base degrees that opens doors to several huge opportunities.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, BCom becomes even more exciting with the addition of an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/what-is-acca-a-complete-guide\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ACCA qualification<\/a>. Being one of the most respected accounting credentials, it aligns perfectly with BCom, which is recognized in approximately 180 countries. Hence, learners gain a dual specialization in one go, fast-tracking their careers and helping them soar to new heights.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>An interesting read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/acca-papers-integrated-with-bcom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How Online BCom with ACCA Paper Integration Offers Financial and Career Benefits<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Global Recognition of ACCA&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ACCA being recognized in different countries is one of the main attractions that students prefer this qualification.&nbsp; With an acknowledgement in 180+ countries and a high global acceptance rate, learners seize the opportunity to complete a qualification like this at every chance they get.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Being fully functional in various parts of the world, including the Middle East, the UK, Europe, and the Asia-Pacific, it opens up a vast range of opportunities for candidates to work in different sectors with high earning potential.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Also read: <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/regular-bcom-and-bcom-with-acca-aligned-curriculum\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><strong>Difference Between a Regular BCom and BCom with ACCA aligned curriculum<\/strong><\/a><strong><\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">How BCom + ACCA Strengthens Your Profile&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The powerful combination of BCom and ACCA comes with some built-in advantages in the professional dimension. Below are some of the advantages:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Dual Advantage of Academic &amp; Professional Skills&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Nothing feels better than getting a dual specialization in the place of one. With a BCom with ACCA program, learners can enjoy the best of both worlds. i.e., with the BCom, they are sorted with the foundational knowledge about accounting, finance, taxation, and so on. On the other hand, ACCA is the key to helping learners apply these skills in a real-world business scenario.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Internationally Relevant Knowledge&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike other fields, finance is subject to different sets of regulations in various countries. However, in three years, apart from just delving into the basics of taxation and regulations through BCom, learners are given the opportunity to focus on IFRS (International Financial Reporting Standards), which are used by most countries worldwide, along with the additional ACCA qualification.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Higher Employability&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Indians can work abroad with ACCA certifications because employers prefer candidates who possess both expertise and exposure, thereby choosing them as able employees. The BCom + ACCA qualification is the way to go because it is not just a degree, but a globally respected certification.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Worth a read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/how-to-become-an-accountant\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">How to become an Accountant?<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Exemptions and Faster Progress&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>With several subjects being overlapped, learners can complete ACCA alongside BCom since they both root from the same field. This added advantage will help students to have exemptions in ACCA exams. Further, this will fast-track the qualification sooner and the ACCA global job prospects will flow towards the learner&#8217;s direction.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Industry Alignment&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>ACCA is industry-aligned, and the course structure is proof that it revolves around what a business truly needs to be. It discusses subjects such as financial reporting, auditing, management accounting, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/mba-in-finance-vs-mba-in-fintech\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">corporate finance<\/a>, and strategy. And with a BCom, the student profile will soar high, as it conveys an impression of academic depth and industry demand.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Career Opportunities Abroad with BCom + ACCA&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are wondering why learners opt for a BCom with ACCA, it is because of the wide recognition of ACCA in different countries and the international work opportunities available with a BCom and ACCA. Given the choice to work in around 180 countries with a prestigious degree is the main attraction of this course.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alongside this, the qualification also provides international standards, such as IFRS, compliance, and global taxation. Below are some of the career opportunities that learners can pursue out of this combination:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Job Role<\/strong>\u00a0<\/th><th><strong>Industry<\/strong>\u00a0<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Audit and Assurance<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Big Four firms (PwC, Deloitte, EY, KPMG), mid-tier audit firms&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Taxation and Compliance<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Consulting firms, MNCs, financial advisory&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Financial Accounting &amp; Reporting<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Banking, manufacturing, FMCG, global corporations&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Corporate Finance<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Investment banking, private equity, multinational companies&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Management &amp; Business Consulting<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Consulting firms, IT services, strategy advisory firms&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Risk and Advisory Services<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Risk management firms, Big Four, insurance companies&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Banking &amp; Financial Services<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>Commercial banks, investment banks, wealth management firms&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Financial Analysis &amp; Planning<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>IT, e-commerce, FMCG, tech startups&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Countries Where BCom + ACCA Works Best&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The ACCA qualification is recognized in over 180 countries, which enhances candidates&#8217; chances of securing greater employment opportunities. Below are some leading countries where the BCom + ACCA combination is most effective.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>UK &amp; Europe\u00a0\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Middle East (UAE, Saudi Arabia, Qatar)\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Canada &amp; Australia\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Singapore &amp; Hong Kong\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>India\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Must-read: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/branches-of-accounting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Branches of accounting: Purpose and types<\/a>\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Salary Expectations Abroad&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As previously discussed, different countries have varying international accounting regulations. And hence, as a matter of fact, the salary range and other factors will also result in a significant variation of the currency valuation. Below is a glimpse of the salary range at the expected career level.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th><strong>Country\/Region<\/strong>\u00a0<\/th><th><strong>Salary Range (Annually)<\/strong>\u00a0<\/th><th><strong>Career Level<\/strong>\u00a0<\/th><\/tr><\/thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>UK<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>\u00a328,000 \u2013 \u00a355,000&nbsp;<\/td><td>Early-career professionals&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Middle East<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>AED 120,000 \u2013 200,000&nbsp;<\/td><td>Mid-level roles&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Singapore<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>SGD 50,000 \u2013 90,000&nbsp;<\/td><td>Varies by role\/experience&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Canada<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>CAD 50,000 \u2013 80,000&nbsp;<\/td><td>Entry to mid-level roles&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><tr><td><strong>Australia<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/td><td>AUD 60,000 \u2013 90,000&nbsp;<\/td><td>Entry to mid-level roles&nbsp;<\/td><\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Conclusion&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hope this blog has hit all the sweet spots for learners who have been looking forward to understanding the requirements, salary, best countries to work in, and more, with a BCom + ACCA accreditation. Being a highly demanded program, students are on the lookout for the best university that provides them with the professional edge on a global scale.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking forward to working abroad with ACCA certifications? But have no time due to full-time jobs or other commitments? Then, an online BCom with ACCA program will be the best fit for you.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Online Manipal<\/a>, Manipal Academy of Higher Education has an interesting combination of online <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/online-bcom-professional-mahe\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">BCom with ACCA<\/a>, many dreams are going to bloom into success. With this integration, students will be able to give up 9 paper exemptions and be recognized in over 180 countries.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next time, when you see a job profile stating \u201cACCA jobs in the UK for Indians\u201d, you could be the one giving it a go. Click here to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/all-courses\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">view<\/a> our other online courses.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Is ACCA recognized worldwide?\u00a0<br>\u00a0<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes. ACCA is recognized in over 180 countries, making it one of the globally accepted accounting qualifications.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Can I pursue ACCA alongside BCom?&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes. Several universities and colleges offer the BCom+ACCA program. Further, learners can also register for an ACCA separately while pursuing their BCom.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. Do I need additional qualifications to work abroad after ACCA?&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Apart from some countries, such as the USA and Canada, most countries accept the ACCA program as it is, without any additional requirements.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. What kinds of jobs can I get abroad with BCom + ACCA?&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of the career options that can be explored abroad are:&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Audit\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Taxation\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Financial reporting\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Corporate finance\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Consulting and banking\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The industries that can be ventured into are:&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Big Four firms\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>MNCs\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>IT companies\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>FMCG\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. What is the average salary of ACCA professionals abroad?&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Salaries vary by country and experience level. For example:&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>UK: \u00a328,000\u2013\u00a355,000\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>UAE: AED 120,000\u2013200,000\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Singapore: SGD 50,000\u201390,000\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Canada: CAD 50,000\u201380,000\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Australia: AUD 60,000\u201390,000\u00a0<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Is BCom with ACCA better than doing only BCom?&nbsp;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes. While BCom gives you academic knowledge, ACCA adds a professional, globally recognized edge. Together, they make your profile stronger and more competitive in both domestic and international job markets.&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Is moving abroad the new fashion now? It certainly appears to be a trend that everyone is following. We bet that everyone will have at least one close-knit loved one who has moved abroad or is in the process of doing so. However, most of them go there to study and then seek employment. But [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":126,"featured_media":18370962,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[188],"tags":[19],"class_list":["post-18370696","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-careers","tag-online-degree"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v27.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/product\/yoast-seo-wordpress\/ -->\n<title>How BCom with ACCA Help You Work Abroad | Online Manipal<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Get to know about the BCom with ACCA job prospects in abroad so that it helps you get to know the scope and career advancements\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18370696\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How BCom with ACCA Help You Work Abroad | Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Get to know about the BCom with ACCA job prospects in abroad so that it helps you get to know the scope and career advancements\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/blogs\/bcom-with-acca-help-you-work-abroad\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Online Manipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:publisher\" content=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/onlinemanipal\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:published_time\" content=\"2025-08-27T12:05:00+00:00\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https:\/\/www.onlinemanipal.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/08\/Can-BCom-with-ACCA-Help-You-Work-Abroad_-Exploring-Global-Prospects_.jpg\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"980\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"380\" \/>\n\t<meta property=\"og:image:type\" content=\"image\/jpeg\" \/>\n<meta name=\"author\" content=\"Krishnanjali KU\" \/>\n<meta name=